2.1 Coverage
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers purchases of tickets all over the world The
insurance applies from the time when the cardholder purchases the
ticket(s) and pays for them in full with his/her card.
.br
The insurance covers the purchase of tickets to a minimum price of DKK
200 each (excluding any fees or charges), that the cardholder has paid
for in full with his/her card.
.kp off
.kp on
.sp 3mm
The insurance covers up to five tickets per event. The maximum
compensation payable is DKK 2,000 per ticket and DKK 10,000 per year.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
2.1.1 If the policy holder cancels his/her card, or if the
insurance coverage ceases on account of the working relationship
between &BANKNAVn. and the insurer being terminated or similar,
tickets purchased using the card before the expiry of the agreement
will still be covered in accordance with the present insurance
terms and conditions, up to the date of the event.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
2.1.2 Insured tickets:
.br
Tickets for personal use for events such as concerts, theatrical
performances, sports events, amusement parks and the like, with a
minimum nominal value of DKK 200 each, which have been paid for in
full using the card during the insurance period.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
2.1.3 The coverage does not apply to tickets of the following types:
.br
.of 5mm
*¤Cinema tickets
