3.0 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Under the insurance, compensation will be paid in the amount of the
nominal value of the ticket in the event that the ticket(s) have to be
cancelled or cannot be used if one of the events listed below affects
the insured or his/her immediate family in the Nordic region:
.sp 3mm
.of 5mm
*¤Death
.of
.of 5mm
*¤Acute illness or unexpected and acute deterioration of a chronic illness
.of
.of 5mm
*¤Acute injury
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Damage to the insured's home, business or office, that occurred after
the tickets were paid for and which requires his/her presence
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Requirement to perform military service or jury duty, which cannot be
altered
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤ID card stolen up to 48 hours prior to the event, where the ID card in
question is the only valid identification
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Acute damage to or theft of a vehicle up to 48 hours before the event
which makes transport to the event impossible
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Delay to public transport lasting at least four hours, which results in
the insured being unable to travel to the event
.of
.of 5mm
*¤Collision/accident en route to the event, which requires towing of the
vehicle when the insured is using a private vehicle to travel to the event.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Immediate family: In this context, 'immediate family' is taken to
refer to the insured's partner/life partner/spouse, children
(including adoptive children), children-in-law, grandchildren, step
children, step-children-in-law, parents, parents-in-law, grandparents,
step-parents, step-parents-in-law, siblings, brothers and
sisters-in-law.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
3.1 Exceptions
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance does not cover cancellation resulting from:
.sp 3mm
.of 5mm
*¤Treatment/operation/health cure or similar that was planned or could
have been foreseen/expected before the tickets were purchased.
.of
.of 5mm
*¤Any illness/condition that the insured was aware of and which
constituted a significant risk that it would not be possible to attend
the event.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
