duty, written documentation of same must be provided.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤In the event of accident involving or theft of a vehicle, written
documentation of same must be provided
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤In the event of delays to public transport, written documentation of the
delay must be provided.
.of
.of 5mm
*¤Any other document the insurer considers necessary to approve the claim
and the associated compensation.
